### Variables
@host = http://localhost:5000
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/health

### 1. Register a new user
# Response includes success flag and userId (optional)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Test123!"
}

### 2. Login – obtain access and refresh tokens
# Save the access token as @token and refresh token as @refreshToken for later requests
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "Test123!"
}
> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.accessToken);
    client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.refreshToken);
    client.global.set("userId", response.body.userId);
%}

### 3. Refresh token – get a new access token
POST {{host}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 4. Logout – revoke the current refresh token
POST {{host}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============ Users ============

### Get all users (requires authentication)
GET {{host}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get current user profile
GET {{host}}/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get user by ID
GET {{host}}/api/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update user (only provide fields to change)
PUT {{host}}/api/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "username": "newusername"
}

### Delete user (admin only in some implementations)
DELETE {{host}}/api/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============ API Keys ============

### Create an API key
# Response: { "key": "base64-string" }
POST {{host}}/api/apikeys
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List user's API keys
# Response: array of ApiKeyDto objects
GET {{host}}/api/apikeys
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============ Sessions ============

### List active sessions
GET {{host}}/api/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Revoke a session (replace {{sessionId}} with actual GUID)
DELETE {{host}}/api/sessions/{{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============ Audit Logs (Admin Only) ============

### Get audit logs with pagination
# Query parameters: page (default 1), pageSize (default 50)
GET {{host}}/api/auditlogs?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============ File Upload ============

### Upload a file (multipart/form-data)
POST {{host}}/api/files/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Sample file content.
------WebKitFormBoundary--